column3: The frequency is some where in the mid frequency range (1-4KHz). One impact noise which is prominent.
Has that characteristic delay like quality of certain thunder. The crackle sounds more realistic than track 2.
Good pattern but goes a bit electric-y towards the end
Started realistically, but then some jumps in the audio made it unnatural
Temporal fluctuation sounds wrong : loudest comes too late.
the initial crack has enough low end and rolling transients give a more plausible feeling of thunder than 4 and 2 to me
The artificially created repeats/delays mimic the rolling of thunder relatively well.
it s quite realistic but a bit too long
wow and flutter type of sounds make it sound implausible
